## Feature Matrix

For comparing 3+ options across multiple features:

```svg
<!-- Column headers -->
<text x="350" y="140" class="option-name" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18"
      fill="var(--accent)">[Option A]</text>
<text x="600" y="140" class="option-name" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18"
      fill="var(--secondary)">[Option B]</text>
<text x="850" y="140" class="option-name" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18"
      fill="var(--muted)">[Option C]</text>

<!-- Header underline -->
<line x1="250" y1="155" x2="950" y2="155" stroke="var(--muted)" stroke-width="1" />

<!-- Row 1 -->
<text x="120" y="200" class="criterion">[Feature 1]</text>
<!-- Check (has feature) -->
<circle cx="350" cy="195" r="10" fill="var(--positive)" />
<text x="350" y="200" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="700">&#10003;</text>
<!-- Check -->
<circle cx="600" cy="195" r="10" fill="var(--positive)" />
<text x="600" y="200" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="700">&#10003;</text>
<!-- X (missing feature) -->
<circle cx="850" cy="195" r="10" fill="var(--neutral)" />
<text x="850" y="200" text-anchor="middle" fill="white" font-size="14" font-weight="700">&#10007;</text>

<line x1="80" y1="220" x2="1000" y2="220" stroke="var(--light-bg)" stroke-width="1" />

<!-- Continue rows, spacing ~50px -->
```

